Skill Bonus	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:UldrasRaceTrait.RaceTrait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Uldras can see in the dark up to 120 feet. Darkvision is black and white only, but it is otherwise like normal sight, and uldras can function just fi ne with no light at all.	KEY:Uldras ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|120|TYPE=Racial																		SOURCEPAGE:Fro	
